# 🤖 Online Chatbot System

## 📌 Overview

This project is a console-based chatbot system built using Java and Object-Oriented Programming concepts.
It follows a structured design similar to a Document Editor system.

---

## 🧠 Features

* Send user messages
* Automatic bot replies
* Chat history storage
* Delete messages
* Input validation

---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

```
com.ChatBot
│
├── main
│   └── MainApp.java
│
├── model
│   ├── Message.java (abstract)
│   ├── UserMessage.java
│   ├── BotMessage.java
│   ├── ChatSession.java
│   └── User.java
│
├── service
│   └── ChatService.java
│
└── util
    └── Validator.java
```

---

## 🔧 OOP Concepts Used

* **Abstraction** → Message class
* **Encapsulation** → Private variables
* **Inheritance** → UserMessage, BotMessage
* **Polymorphism** → display() method
* **Separation of Concerns** → Service layer

---

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Compile all Java files
2. Run `MainApp.java`
3. Start chatting in console

